MaildirStore personal-local
Path ~/.mail/personal/
Inbox ~/.mail/personal/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim
Trash None

IMAPStore personal-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
UserCmd "cat ~/.mail/personal-username"
PassCmd "pass $(cat ~/.mail/personal-username)@gmail.com"
TLSType IMAPS

Channel personal
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
SyncState *
Patterns ![Gmail]* INBOX "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Spam" "[Gmail]/Trash"

MaildirStore upmail-local
Path ~/.mail/upmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/upmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim
Trash None

IMAPStore upmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
UserCmd "cat ~/.mail/upmail-username"
PassCmd "pass $(cat ~/.mail/upmail-username)"
TLSType IMAPS

Channel upmail
Far :upmail-remote:
Near :upmail-local:
SyncState *
Patterns ![Gmail]* INBOX "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Spam" "[Gmail]/Trash"

Group boxes
Channels personal upmail

